    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/1c2f7a0ad0e125c16326478b0538d6f2.poster.avif?t=1772468646\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/1c2f7a0ad0e125c16326478b0538d6f2.webm?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/1c2f7a0ad0e125c16326478b0538d6f2.mp4?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《Corner Shop: Nightshift》是一款设定在濒临倒闭的便利店里的第一人称叙事恐怖模拟游戏。你将扮演亚当·卡拉汉，试图把自己的人生重新拼起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情模式（Story Mode）：</strong> 以平均节奏游玩约 <strong>15 小时</strong>，根据玩家选择有 <strong>4 种结局</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽模式（Endless Mode）：</strong> 无尽玩法，侧重于扩建与经营店铺，并持续加入恐怖要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主播模式（Streamer Mode）：</strong> 与 <strong>Twitch</strong> 联动，观众可在地图上触发行动，包括顾客与恐怖事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/03a66340a134eb9d36894165e0b1938f.poster.avif?t=1772468646\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/03a66340a134eb9d36894165e0b1938f.webm?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/03a66340a134eb9d36894165e0b1938f.mp4?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>夜班与支离破碎的人生。停电、警报、令人不安的顾客把你拖进一场无法逃脱的谜局。寻找真相，控制压力，别让偏执占上风。吃药。继续撑下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/ccb08461a9757f16f235a2af2c457cf8.poster.avif?t=1772468646\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/ccb08461a9757f16f235a2af2c457cf8.webm?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/ccb08461a9757f16f235a2af2c457cf8.mp4?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>补货上架、清理卫生、收货、扫码结账，给顾客提供零食、三明治和烤肉卷。用摄像头、警报和更牢固的门锁升级店铺。管理你的时间、金钱与理智。药可不会自己付钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/6e3ab573bf8f6ef5e03050b27801f29b.poster.avif?t=1772468646\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/6e3ab573bf8f6ef5e03050b27801f29b.webm?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306990/extras/6e3ab573bf8f6ef5e03050b27801f29b.mp4?t=1772468646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你扮演亚当·卡拉汉。他的妻子消失了，女儿被带走，他的人生正在崩塌。他靠夜班证明自己还能重新开始，但这家店不断把他的过去拽回眼前，混乱无序，失控难挡。你的选择将决定你会发现什么，以及最终抵达哪一种结局。</p>",
